@startuml
title Webhook Delivery Retry And Manual Retry

actor "Gateway Worker" as Worker
actor Ops
participant "Webhook Delivery Service" as DeliveryService
participant "Webhook Ops Controller" as WebhookOps
participant "Audit Service" as Audit
participant "Merchant Webhook URL" as MerchantWebhook
database PostgreSQL as DB

Worker -> DeliveryService: deliver_due_webhooks(now)
DeliveryService -> DB: find webhook_events(status=PENDING, next_retry_at<=now)
DB --> DeliveryService: due event
DeliveryService -> DB: load merchant + active credential
DeliveryService -> MerchantWebhook: POST signed webhook payload
MerchantWebhook --> DeliveryService: HTTP 500
DeliveryService -> DB: insert webhook_delivery_attempts(FAILED)
DeliveryService -> DB: update webhook_events(PENDING, next_retry_at)

Worker -> DeliveryService: repeated delivery attempts
DeliveryService -> DB: attempt_count reaches 4
DeliveryService -> DB: update webhook_events(FAILED, next_retry_at=null)

Ops -> WebhookOps: POST /v1/ops/webhooks/{event_id}/retry\nactor context
WebhookOps -> DeliveryService: manual_retry(event_id, audit_context)
DeliveryService -> MerchantWebhook: POST signed webhook payload
MerchantWebhook --> DeliveryService: HTTP 2xx
DeliveryService -> DB: insert webhook_delivery_attempts(SUCCESS)
DeliveryService -> DB: update webhook_events(DELIVERED)
DeliveryService -> Audit: record WEBHOOK_MANUAL_RETRY
Audit -> DB: insert audit_logs
WebhookOps --> Ops: 200 WebhookRetryResponse(status=DELIVERED)
@enduml
